            "is_constituent_info": false,
            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* Sustains critical high-tech aerospace work in MD-06, where NASA Science has invested over $318,000 recently with local firms like CSP Enterprises, LLC and Cryo Associates Inc.\n* Protects Maryland's STEM workforce and innovation pipeline from further disruption following the instability of FY 2026 funding cuts.\n* Reaffirms U.S. leadership in the global space race against China by funding peer-reviewed Decadal Survey priorities that no private entity can replicate.\n* Provides a high return on investment, with every dollar in NASA spending returning roughly three dollars to the regional and national economy.",
            "rationale": "Rationale is based on MD-06 local spending data ($318k total) and specific contractors (CSP Enterprises, Cryo Associates) mentioned in the NASA spending context. It also leverages strategic talking points regarding U.S. leadership, the FY2026 funding restoration, and the 3:1 economic ROI.",
